"(define (atom->macro atom)
  (let-values ([(pict Hlocs) (atom->fp-pict+Hlocs atom)])
    ;; CAUTION use the pict-height/width as macro size
    ;; FIXME this is exact, e.g. 6/5
    (let ([h (pict-height pict)]
          [w (pict-width pict)])
      ;; get the location of pins
      (Macro w h Hlocs))))"
